Package org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.digitalarchitecture.server

Class ReferenceDataRESTServices

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.digitalarchitecture.server.ReferenceDataRESTServices
public class ReferenceDataRESTServices extends Object
ReferenceDataRESTServices provides the API operations to create and maintain lists of valid value definitions grouped into a valid value set. Both valid value definitions and valid value sets have the same attributes and so inherit from ValidValue where all the attributes are defined.

A set is just grouping of valid values. Valid value definitions and set can be nested many times in other valid value sets.
